comments: Doncic (DAL) slightly extends his forearm into Hollis-Jefferson's (TOR) front, but the contact is marginal and does not affect his ability to defend.
Hollis-Jefferson (TOR) and Doncic (DAL) make mutually marginal foot to foot contact.
Hollis-Jefferson (TOR) swipes down and makes contact to the ball during Doncic's (DAL) driving shot attempt.
Siakam (TOR) is firming up and makes marginal contact with Finney-Smith (DAL) while setting the screen.
Porzingis (DAL) briefly grasps Hollis-Jefferson's (TOR) arm during the rebound, the contact does not affect Hollis-Jefferson (TOR) as he dives for the loose ball on his own accord.
Anunoby (TOR) dislodges Curry (DAL) from his legally obtained position.
Powell (TOR) commits a take foul on Doncic (DAL).
Kleber (DAL) maintains a legal guarding position during Siakam's (TOR) driving shot attempt.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) and Hollis-Jefferson (TOR) briefly engage and disengage during the rebound.
Hollis-Jefferson (TOR) reaches around Doncic (DAL) and makes slight contact to his arm.
VanVleet (TOR) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
Doncic (DAL) splits his feet at the start of his dribble.
VanVleet (TOR) and Finney-Smith (DAL) briefly engage and disengage during the rebound.
Doncic (DAL) moves laterally into the Powell's (TOR) path and the body contact that occurs is deemed marginal. Powell (TOR) changes direction and moves though the contact as he continues his drive.
Hollis-Jefferson (TOR) is imminently exiting the lane within three seconds.
Siakam (TOR) commits a take foul on Doncic (DAL).
VanVleet (TOR) is in the lane for longer than three seconds without actively guarding an opponent.
Powell (TOR) cleanly deflects the pass intended for Finney-Smith (DAL).
